OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FA victim of the infected blood scandal
OL,7,Fhas said he feels his family is being
OL,8,F"penalised" financially because he
OL,9,Fhasn't died yet.
OL,11,FKirk Ellis, 44, was born with
OL,12,Fhaemophilia and received contaminated
OL,13,Fblood when he was 14 months old. He
OL,14,Fwas later diagnosed with hepatitis C
OL,15,Faged 15.
OL,17,FNow Kirk says his wife and children
OL,18,Fwill only receive regular widow's
OL,19,Fpayments - financial compensation - if
OL,20,Fhe dies before the end of this month.
