OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FInstead, they will receive a one off
OL,7,Fpayment when he dies - something he
OL,8,Fsays has taken away his family's long
OL,9,Fterm "financial security".
OL,11,FKirk has suffered a lifetime of mental
OL,12,Fand physical ill health, and the
OL,13,Feffects continue to this day. After
OL,14,Freceiving treatment for hepatitis C,
OL,15,FKirk was unable to return to work and
OL,16,Fas a result has no pension.
