OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FHe says the government's decision to
OL,7,Fremove regular payments to families
OL,8,Fafter their loved ones die after 31
OL,9,FMarch has left him feeling as though
OL,10,Fhe is 'worth more' to his family's
OL,11,Ffinancial security if he died now.
OL,13,FLast year after a six year inquiry,
OL,14,Fthe UK Government announced a
OL,15,Fcompensation package for victims of
OL,16,Finfected blood and their families.
