OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FThe UK Government has set aside #11.8
OL,7,Fbillion for victims and their loved
OL,8,Fones. But according to the body that
OL,9,Fmakes those awards only #44 million
OL,10,Fhas been paid out so far.
OL,12,FHaemophilia Wales says it could take
OL,13,Fup to six years for everyone to
OL,14,Freceive their payments, meaning some
OL,15,Fbereaved partners will die without
OL,16,Fcompensation.
