OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FKirk says he feels the compensation
OL,7,Fscheme does not recognise the impact
OL,8,Fthe hepatitis C diagnosis and
OL,9,Fsubsequent treatment has had on his
OL,10,Ffamily and their finances.
OL,12,FHe says that the end of March is the
OL,13,Fcut off date for bereaved partners to
OL,14,Fhave a choice in how they receive
OL,15,Ffinancial compensation.
OL,17,FInstead of being given the option of
OL,18,Fmonthly payments or a lump sum, only
OL,19,Fthe latter option will be on offer.
