OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,F"My wife won't be given that choice,
OL,7,Fshe will be given a lump sum of what's
OL,8,Fleft of my pot - which for me isn't
OL,9,Ffinancial security, it isn't what I
OL,10,Ffought for years ago. We campaigned
OL,11,Ffor it, we were taking legal action,"
OL,12,Fsaid the father of three.
OL,14,F"It's the financial security, it's a
OL,15,Fmonthly payment, you're not going to
OL,16,Fhave to manage the money yourself to
OL,17,Fmake sure it lasts. It's what we
OL,18,Ffought for, the way we looked at it is
OL,19,Fthat it's a widows pension, that's
OL,20,Fbeen taken away.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
