OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,F"I haven't been able to work, I
OL,7,Fhaven't been able to get a pension so
OL,8,Fthere's no financial security for my
OL,9,Fwife and my kids because I am still
OL,10,Falive.
OL,12,F"I feel like I am being penalised
OL,13,Fbecause I haven't passed away yet. I
OL,14,Fam actually worth more to my family's
OL,15,Ffinancial security if I passed away
OL,16,Fnow, today or tomorrow, or before the
OL,17,Fend of March than if I die after.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/13
