OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,F"The sad truth is that a compensation
OL,7,Fscheme which was supposed to be set up
OL,8,Fto compensate us for wrongdoing has
OL,9,Fmade me feel like that."
OL,11,FKirk says that the realisation his
OL,12,Ffamily will now get different
OL,13,Fcompensation has left him feeling that
OL,14,Fthe government are "cutting dying
OL,15,Fvictims short".
OL,17,FThose affected by the blood infection
OL,18,Fscandal mainly contracted HIV or
OL,19,Fhepatitis as a result, with financial
OL,20,Fcompensation varying between both.
