OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FThere are also discrepancies in how
OL,7,Fthe treatment on offer at the time
OL,8,Fimpacted people's lives. Kirk says
OL,9,Fthat because he had a mixture of both
OL,10,Fold and new treatments (post 2016) he
OL,11,Fwas unable to return to work and these
OL,12,Fdifferences have not been considered
OL,13,Fby the government.
OL,15,F"They've stuck us all in one pot
OL,16,Fbasically. I feel worthless again.
OL,17,FIt's just a constant worry and that's
OL,18,Fwhy I wanted the financial support for
OL,19,Fmy wife."
