OL,6,FHe says that the decision to change
OL,7,Fthe way compensation is paid to
OL,8,Ffamilies depending on when the
OL,9,Faffected person dies is "unfair".
OL,11,FKirk says he hoped the fight for
OL,12,Fjustice was won with the result of the
OL,13,Finquiry but now he is fighting for
OL,14,F"financial security" for his family
OL,15,Fafter his death.
