OL,3,CInfected blood scandal victim says he
OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FHis wife will still receive
OL,7,Fcompensation when Kirk dies, but he
OL,8,Fsays it will be less than the support
OL,9,Fpayments she would receive each month
OL,10,Ffor the rest of her life had that
OL,11,Fstill been an option.
OL,13,FThe UK Government says that bereaved
OL,14,Fpartners will be able to apply for
OL,15,Fcompensation through periodic payments
OL,16,Fbut Kirk says the amount means his
OL,17,Fwife will still be worse off from the
OL,18,Fend of the month.
