OL,4,Cis 'worth more financially if he died'
OL,6,FA spokesperson said: "While no amount
OL,7,Fof compensation will make up for the
OL,8,Fsuffering people have endured, we have
OL,9,Fheard calls from the community and
OL,10,Facted by paying over #44 million in
OL,11,Fcompensation payments and over a
OL,12,Fbillion pounds in interim payments so
OL,13,Ffar.
OL,15,F"And the Budget set aside #11.8
OL,16,Fbillion to compensate victims of
OL,17,Finfected blood in what is one of the
OL,18,Flargest compensation schemes in recent
OL,19,Fhistory."
